short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhance your NFT trading with the Tiny Astro Extension

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Tiny Astro extension allows you to purchase listings from various marketplaces with one click.

Future functionality may include: NFT rarity ranking when browsing marketplaces, analytics and trends, alpha calls
